  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* fix(xml): reject invalid XML element and attribute names by @lawrence3699 in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/536\r\n* Bump github.com/goccy/go-json from 0.10.5 to 0.10.6 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/530\r\n* man: use SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH if defined by @guilherme-puida in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/540\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @lawrence3699 made their first contribution in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/536\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/compare/v3.8.0...v3.8.1",
